title: [Czeroth Labyrinth, Nexus]
description: Several tunnels crisscross through this jagged black granite nexus. Embedded into the rock, iridescent crimson crystals peek out of crevices like fireflies in a black forest.   A pool of thick bluish green goop occupies the center of the intersection, reeking strongly of decomposition and sewage.
paths: Obvious exits: northeast, southeast, southwest, northwest
